    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/c3089161000291bec779b31006ee220e.poster.avif?t=1751665954\" width=572 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/c3089161000291bec779b31006ee220e.webm?t=1751665954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>体验最新的《House Flipper》探索更多的农场音效。<br>将你的生活与动物们连接得更加紧密。<br>建造围栏，饲养猪、羊、鸡等。<br>农耕冒险即将开始！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/de4a682cd2ccf380b32d49d3f71c856e.poster.avif?t=1751665954\" width=572 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/de4a682cd2ccf380b32d49d3f71c856e.webm?t=1751665954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你想在装修后的家中再添一间房间吗？<br>你是否梦想拥有一个车库？<br>《Farm DLC》满足你的愿望。<br>新的房屋扩建机制将彻底改变你的装修方式！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/296e83ba973425e5a58845dcdde4f709.poster.avif?t=1751665954\" width=572 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/296e83ba973425e5a58845dcdde4f709.webm?t=1751665954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>饿了？我去弄点吃的！你更喜欢玉米还是西红柿？<br>无论你种什么，你都必须照顾好你的蔬菜。<br>有许多工具和一系列新的农业技能可以帮助你进行农业生产。<br>修整土地，保证水源充足，在不知不觉中收获满满！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/003663f226b4d772f99dbd5e764eff07.poster.avif?t=1751665954\" width=572 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832960/extras/003663f226b4d772f99dbd5e764eff07.webm?t=1751665954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>视察农场不仅是一种责任，更是一种乐趣！<br>召唤你最喜欢的马，骑上它在你的土地上闲逛。<br>这只是冒险的开始，枫叶村在等着你！<br><br>农场 DLC 包括：<br>- 10 个包含故事情节的任务订单！<br>- 独特环境中的 9 个农场建筑！<br>- 3 块空地供您建造！<br>- 7 种激动人心的机制，包括扩建房屋！<br>- 超过 1500 种农场主题物品！<br>- 农场动物，如牛、羊、鸡等等！<br>- 种植你喜欢的植物！",
